From: hpages at fhcrc.org (=?windows-1252?Q?Herv=E9_Pag=E8s?=)
Date: Mon, 22 Jul 2013 11:47:14 -0700
Subject: [Bioc-devel] IntAE buffers needs to be freed or not??
In-Reply-To: <DUB114-W692D9DC30A1ED7E0B3648856E0@phx.gbl>
References: <DUB114-W112F375B92F030B4EA85FFC85630@phx.gbl>,
	<51E9D44A.3020003@fhcrc.org>
	<DUB114-W692D9DC30A1ED7E0B3648856E0@phx.gbl>
